Version of the model regrouping variables according to their source

MODFLOW-2005 simulates steady and nonsteady flow in an irregularly shaped flow system in which aquifer layers can be confined or unconfined. Flow from external stresses such as flow to wells and areal recharge or evapotranspiration can be simulated (usgs.gov. 2019)
